Prohibition= Strong Prohibiton= Mustn't = You Mustn't smoke in class
Obligation= Strong Obligation= Must = You must study harder if you want to pass
          = Less Obligation = Have to= I won't go to the party because i have to work
                                       I have to wake up Early in the morning
No obligation= Don't have to = You Don't have to wear uniform to go to high school
               Don't Need to
Advice= S
